        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 126−130. Laminamichaelia furcula sp. nov. 126—Tarsus II (2B), Tibia II (2B); 127—2 slightly bent claws and a setulated empodium; 128—Tritonymph, venter, 6−7 genital setae per valve, 5−6 anal setae per valve; 129—Deutonymph, venter, 4 genital setae per valve, 4−6 anal setae per valve; 130—Protonymph, venter, 1 genital seta per valve, 4 anal setae per valve." ;
