        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 131−132. Laminamichaelia furcula sp. nov. 131—Larva, ventral habitus, slight neotrichy, genital valves absent, 2−3 anal setae per valve; 132—Larva, dorsal habitus, neotrichy. 119−132 from RSA, near Potchefstroom." ;
